{"tid":2214312,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"悟空：「師父，取完經你隨我回花果山吧。」","createTime":"2020-09-23T07:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T05:41:55.000Z","uid":49699,"like":20,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dea80eca6e8c45ebde02f64214283f564386ecfb","tid":2214312,"uid":49699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"沙僧：「二師兄，那個，你還想念高老莊的秀蘭麼？」<br />\n<br />\n八戒看著前面那個扛著金箍棒的背影搖了搖頭。<br />\n<br />\n悟空：「師父，取完經你隨我回花果山吧。」<br />\n<br />\n唐僧：「悟空，你以為我們僅僅是去取經麼？為師要和如來徹夜探討佛法。」<br />\n<br />\n說著羞紅了臉，<br />\n<br />\n卻不知何時，跨下的白龍馬已淚流滿面。"},{"pid":"bcb11a8affdec0acb989980df7591428bce828de","tid":2214312,"uid":49699,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"約好的每週下棋時間，他難得遲到，<br />\n<br />\n他看著他有些異樣的神色什麼都沒問<br />\n<br />\n。突然他開口說：<br />\n<br />\n「我兒子剛才說，要和你兒子去荷蘭結婚，我答應了。」<br />\n<br />\n他微愣了一下，點點頭。<br />\n<br />\n下完棋，兩個人都坐著沒動。<br />\n<br />\n沉默良久，他輕嘆口氣：<br />\n<br />\n「當初我們要是勇敢一點，也就沒這倆小子什麼事了。」<br />\n<br />\n他笑笑：「青出於藍。」"},{"pid":"0e71fafe321915b97c4822f9dac1128d7b756efb","tid":2214312,"uid":247048,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0860bf5f03bbae25b6b795017ab714d0d62c2269","tid":2214312,"uid":160798,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgBiZwF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgBiZwF.jpg&h=8edb388a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5d7b2defab4ace2e445de325b57935e3fdb1630","tid":2214312,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"第一個唔識睇，可否指點下"},{"pid":"0ebc17a3812ebb0db6662d7cd4a433e7dff078bc","tid":2214312,"uid":216592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/